## Fonts - Commercial License Required

This theme is designed to use the Doves Type family (Text and Headline variants). 
These fonts are NOT included with this theme and require separate commercial licensing.

- Doves Type is a registered trademark of TypeSpec Ltd.
- The fonts must be licensed separately from TypeSpec: https://typespec.co.uk/doves-type/
- Font licensing options include desktop, web, app, and ePub usage
- The theme will not function as designed without properly licensed copies of these fonts

## Additional Notes

1. The theme's CSS contains references to Doves Type but does not include the font files
2. Sample content and documentation may show the fonts in use, but these are for demonstration purposes only
3. The MIT License applies solely to the theme code, templates, and structure
4. Users must ensure they have appropriate licenses for any fonts used with this theme

For font licensing inquiries, please contact Typespec Ltd directly.
